---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: normalize_help_output(&stdout)
---
Print the current Spotify queue

Usage: spotuify queue [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  add   Add an item to the current queue
  help  Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format [default: table] [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
